cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper focuses on music emotion detection and uses audio and lyrics data to achieve this goal. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper uses Natural Language Processing techniques to process the lyrics data and Deep Learning architectures to classify emotions. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper uses Music Information Retrieval techniques to process the audio data and extract vocal features. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with both audio and lyrics data, which are two types of multimedia data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses Deep Learning techniques to classify emotions, which falls under the scope of Artificial Intelligence.
